Output media/hero.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Padding 24

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "whip-claude list"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Hide
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "whip-claude demo cosmic"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
